# Data Tables (list views)

Use for **entity list tables** ‚Äî not `form-table` in dialogs (see [`forms-layout.mdc`](forms-layout.mdc)).

## Required components

- [`DataTable.svelte`](src/lib/components/DataTable.svelte) ‚Äî wrapper, filtering, pagination, serial #, sticky columns
- [`DataTableColumn.svelte`](src/lib/components/DataTableColumn.svelte) ‚Äî one per data column

## Column order (left to right)

| Position | Content | Sticky |
|----------|---------|--------|
| 1 | Row actions (`IconActionButton`) | yes (`5.5rem`) |
| 2 | Serial `#` (continuous across pages on filtered rows) | yes |
| 3+ | Data columns ‚Äî mark primary name/title with `firstData` | first data column sticky |

## Header filters

- Each `DataTableColumn` header is an `input` with `placeholder={label}`
- Client-side, case-insensitive contains on `filterText(row)`
- Actions and `#` columns have no filter input
- Serial numbers reflect the **filtered** set and **continue across pages** (e.g. page 2 with page size 20 starts at 21)

## Pagination

- Built into `DataTable` ‚Äî default **20** rows per page
- Page size selector: **10 / 20 / 50** (`pageSizeOptions` prop)
- Filters apply first, then pagination; changing filters or page size resets to page 1
- Footer hidden when there are no rows; shows page controls + `1‚Äì20 of 142` range text

## Actions snippet

```svelte
<DataTable rows={items} rowKey={(row) => row.id} emptyMessage="No items yet.">
	{#snippet actions({ row })}
		<IconActionButton label="Edit" variant="secondary" onclick={() => dialog?.open(row)}>
			<Pencil class="h-4 w-4" />
		</IconActionButton>
	{/snippet}

	<DataTableColumn label="Name" firstData filterText={(row) => row.name}>
		{#snippet children({ row })}
			{row.name}
		{/snippet}
	</DataTableColumn>
</DataTable>
```

## Rules

- Row actions in the **first** column only ‚Äî see [`action-buttons.mdc`](action-buttons.mdc)
- `filterText` must return plain searchable text (join nested lists with spaces for complex cells)
- Optional non-sticky columns before `firstData` (e.g. icon/image) ‚Äî do **not** set `firstData` on them
- Empty state: `emptyMessage` on `DataTable` (single row, full colspan)
- Wrapper styling is built into `DataTable` ‚Äî do not duplicate `overflow-x-auto rounded-box border`

Filter logic: [`src/lib/utils/table-filter.ts`](src/lib/utils/table-filter.ts)

Sticky CSS: `.data-table .sticky-col-*` in [`src/routes/layout.css`](src/routes/layout.css)
